OL,3,CDriver who killed eight-month-old baby
OL,4,Cin pram has sentence reduced
OL,6,FA driver who struck and killed an
OL,7,Feight-month-old baby in her pram
OL,8,Foutside a hospital has had her prison
OL,9,Fsentence reduced at the Court of
OL,10,FAppeal, in what judges described as a
OL,11,F"truly tragic" case.
OL,13,FBridget Curtis pressed down on the
OL,14,Faccelerator of her automatic BMW 520d
OL,15,Fcar after stopping outside Withybush
OL,16,FHospital in Haverfordwest,
OL,17,FPembrokeshire, on June 21 2023,
OL,18,Fcausing it to mount a kerb and collide
OL,19,Fwith the pushchair of Mabli Cariad
OL,20,FHall.
