OL,3,CDriver who killed eight-month-old baby
OL,4,Cin pram has sentence reduced
OL,6,FMabli, who had just said a final
OL,7,Fgoodbye to her paternal grandmother
OL,8,FBetty Hall, who was receiving end-of-
OL,9,Flife care at the hospital, sustained
OL,10,Ffatal head injuries and died in
OL,11,Fhospital days later.
OL,13,FCurtis, who was 69 at the time of the
OL,14,Foffence and is now 71, pleaded guilty
OL,15,Fto causing death by dangerous driving
OL,16,Flast September and was jailed for four
OL,17,Fyears at Swansea Crown Court in
OL,18,FJanuary.
