OL,4,Cin pram has sentence reduced
OL,6,FMr Justice Butcher, sitting with Lord
OL,7,FJustice Bean and Judge Richard Marks
OL,8,FKC, said: "We say at once that this is
OL,9,Fa truly tragic case.
OL,11,F"We have read the very moving victim
OL,12,Fpersonal statements of Mabli's
OL,13,Fparents, expressing their grief at the
OL,14,Fdeath of their beloved baby.
OL,16,F"No one could fail to sympathise with
OL,17,Fthem for the appalling loss that they
OL,18,Fhave sustained."
