OL,3,CDriver who killed eight-month-old baby
OL,4,Cin pram has sentence reduced
OL,6,FCurtis, who attended the appeal via
OL,7,Fvideo link from HMP Eastwood Park in
OL,8,FGloucestershire and sat in a
OL,9,Fwheelchair throughout, had no previous
OL,10,Fconvictions at the time of the
OL,11,Fincident and had held a clean driving
OL,12,Flicence for more than 50 years.
OL,14,FHer sentencing hearing at Swansea
OL,15,FCrown Court heard that on the day of
OL,16,Fthe collision, she had driven her
OL,17,Fdaughter to an outpatient appointment
OL,18,Fat the hospital.
