OL,3,CDriver who killed eight-month-old baby
OL,4,Cin pram has sentence reduced
OL,6,FWhen her daughter struggled to find
OL,7,Fher handbag in the rear of the car,
OL,8,FCurtis unlocked the door and turned
OL,9,Faround to assist her.
OL,11,FBut as she did so, she pressed down on
OL,12,Fthe accelerator of her car, which had
OL,13,Fbeen left running and was not in park
OL,14,Fmode.
OL,16,FThe car reached speeds of more than
OL,17,F29mph and travelled 28 metres in
OL,18,Faround four seconds, mounting the kerb
OL,19,Fof a grass seating area and causing
OL,20,FMabli to be thrown out of her
OL,21,Fpushchair.
