OL,3,CDriver who killed eight-month-old baby
OL,4,Cin pram has sentence reduced
OL,6,FThe car only stopped when it collided
OL,7,Fwith a tree, having also caused
OL,8,Finjuries to Mabli's father Rob Hall.
OL,10,FMabli, the youngest of six siblings,
OL,11,Freceived treatment at the Withybush
OL,12,FHospital, as well as hospitals in
OL,13,FCardiff and Bristol, dying in the arms
OL,14,Fof her parents on June 25.
OL,16,FHer mother, Gwen Hall, told the
OL,17,Fsentencing hearing that her daughter
OL,18,Fwas "so bright, so beautiful, so full
OL,19,Fof love and life".
