OL,3,CDriver who killed eight-month-old baby
OL,4,Cin pram has sentence reduced
OL,6,FShe said: "She hadn't crawled yet. She
OL,7,Fhad said 'Mama' for the first time
OL,8,Fonly the day before. We had so much
OL,9,Fplanned with her.
OL,11,F"It was nowhere near the time for her
OL,12,Fto be taken away from us. She was my
OL,13,Fbaby. My eight-month-old baby."
OL,15,FJohn Dye, for Curtis, told Swansea
OL,16,FCrown Court that she was a mother-of-
OL,17,Ffour and grandmother of 10, who was
OL,18,F"absolutely devastated" by the
OL,19,Fincident.
