OL,3,CDriver who killed eight-month-old baby
OL,4,Cin pram has sentence reduced
OL,6,FAppearing again for Curtis at the
OL,7,FCourt of Appeal on Tuesday, Mr Dye
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is a tragic case, but the
OL,9,Fissue really was one of pedal
OL,10,Fconfusion."
OL,12,FHe continued: "Objectively, this is
OL,13,Fclearly dangerous driving, but in
OL,14,Fterms of culpability, these four
OL,15,Fseconds of driving were more akin to,
OL,16,Fmaybe not a momentary lapse, but a
OL,17,Flapse of concentration."
OL,19,FCraig Jones, for the Crown Prosecution
OL,20,FService, made no oral submissions to
OL,21,Fthe court.
