OL,3,CDriver who killed eight-month-old baby
OL,4,Cin pram has sentence reduced
OL,6,FReducing the sentence, Mr Justice
OL,7,FButcher said: "True it is that the
OL,8,Fappellant did not intend to cause any
OL,9,Fharm, and true also that the mistake
OL,10,Fwas of a short duration, but the
OL,11,Fdriving was well over the threshold of
OL,12,Fdangerousness."
OL,14,FHe continued that Curtis would have
OL,15,Fknown that she had stopped "in a busy
OL,16,Farea outside a hospital with
OL,17,Fpotentially very vulnerable
OL,18,Fpedestrians around", and that four or
OL,19,Ffive seconds "is far from being a
OL,20,Fnegligible duration".
